---
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<Layout title="About - Dilli Bhaskar">
  <section class="relative z-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto my-12 px-7 lg:px-0">

    <h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">About Me</h1>

    <p class="mb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      I'm an incoming M.A.Sc student in Electrical and Computer Engineering at the
      <a href="https://www.ubc.ca/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline dark:text-blue-400">University of British Columbia</a>,
      advised by <a href="#" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline dark:text-blue-400">Prof. Cyrus Neary</a>.
      I am passionate about building robots that can think like humans, working on reinforcement learning-based control of autonomous systems
      and conducting empirical experiments on continuous control.
    </p>

    <!-- Education -->
    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4 text-xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-100" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Education</h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0"><img src="/assets/images/experiences/ubc_logo.png" alt="UBC" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-white" /></div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold dark:text-neutral-100">M.A.Sc in Electrical and Computer Engineering</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">University of British Columbia (UBC), Vancouver, CA</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">Sep. 2025 – Aug. 2027 · Advisor: Prof. Cyrus Neary</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0"><img src="/assets/images/experiences/TCE-Madurai-Logo.png" alt="TCE" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-white" /></div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold dark:text-neutral-100">B.E. in Mechanical Engineering</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Thiagarajar College of Engineering (TCE), Madurai, IN</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">Aug. 2020 – April 2024 · CGPA: 9.02/10.00 (First Class with Distinction)</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">Department Best Outgoing Student · Advisor: Prof. S. Saravana Perumal</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Research Experience -->
    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4 text-xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-100" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Research Experience</h2>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <img src="/assets/images/experiences/IIT-Madras-Logo.png" alt="IIT Madras" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-white" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold dark:text-neutral-100">Project Associate</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Indian Institute of Technology Madras, Chennai</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">July 2024 – Present · Advisor: Prof. Chandrashekar Lakshminarayanan</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Development of Deep RL based pursuit evasion solver with fixed wing UAV agents.</li>
            <li>Fighter pilot behavior cloning for Deep RL based aerobatic maneuvers.</li>
            <li>Rendering the simulations in Unreal Engine.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <img src="/assets/images/experiences/iitpkd.jpeg" alt="IIT Palakkad" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-white" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold dark:text-neutral-100">Research Intern</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Indian Institute of Technology Palakkad</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">Jan. 2024 – June 2024 · Advisor: Prof. Shaikshavali Chitraganti</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Implemented Deep RL-based motion planners using ROS and Gazebo.</li>
            <li>Tested performance on Sim-to-Real experiments using TurtleBot3.</li>
            <li>Developed an energy-based model using action maximization for exploration.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0"><img src="/assets/images/experiences/TCE-Madurai-Logo.png" alt="TCE" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-white" /></div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold dark:text-neutral-100">Student Researcher — Vision Systems Lab</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Thiagarajar College of Engineering, Madurai</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">Sep. 2022 – Dec. 2023 · Advisor: Prof. S. Saravana Perumaal</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Investigated multi-agent task scheduling using RL to minimize queuing delays.</li>
            <li>Devised a novel path planning algorithm for mobile fulfillment systems using RL.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0"><img src="/assets/images/experiences/TCE-Madurai-Logo.png" alt="TCE" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-white" /></div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold dark:text-neutral-100">Student Researcher — Artificial Intelligence Lab</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Thiagarajar College of Engineering, Madurai</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">Feb. 2022 – Aug. 2022 · Advisor: Prof. M. Suguna</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Developed an object detection model for fire using thermal images.</li>
            <li>Extracted saliency maps using BAS-Net & performed detection using YOLOv7.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>
</Layout>
